column3: “Happy, uplifting, mellow high. Still blazed 2 hours later. Eliminated my headache and backache. No munchies after!”

“Take me to Paradise Sweet Sweet Hawaiian Sunrise! Beautiful, Stanky and Feels Amazingly Floaty in the Head Instantly, Slight Headband. But you can still Concentrate. Slightly Melo Body Feeling. Very Potent. Fast Acting. Makes me wanna Dance to the music.”
“Tastes nice, burns nice and slow. Definitely good bud 😆”
“Got this in the sativa bundle from Pot Cargo.  Bland, weak, and uninspiring.  Would not buy this again.”
“Was wishy-washy on this one at first but love it now. Great smell and taste, fun high.”
“a shorter lasting high but a very fun one, one of my happiest feelings”
“Compact yet very frosted buds. Biggest munchies ever! Cool buzz. Very euphoric.”

“had this strain a few weeks back. anything Hawaiian seems to be very pleasant. kind bud. these were very dense nuggs. rich in flavor....I like participating in reviews on leafly, but some of this is like an 8th or 9th grade lunchroom-WHOA-discussion. its so funny to listen to all the inexperienced people on here, new comers and straight rookies. look everybody, settle down, its just buds. and to be quite frank, marij...”
